defaultGeneral:default We support the overall thrust of the Bill to be deregulatory but do not have the knowledge and experience to comment on the best way to achieve deregulation within the Parliamentary process. However we support the consensus approach used by the Stakeholder Working Group (SWG), which underpins part of the Bill.
