default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWhilst additional regulation may not be in itself a breach of human rights we think that additional regulation by opportunist additions at the last minute into this Bill would not be properly consulted on and examined by the governments own advisers and would be contrary to the rights of our members.
